{"tid":1247894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[公祭]其實梁義士嘅精神為香港日後抗爭運動埋下咗一粒種子","createTime":"2019-06-21T09:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T13:30:36.000Z","uid":59693,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3cbd395aa4feb5c6ec88616e67da51b13c48e2b6","tid":1247894,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:22:15.000Z","msg":"正如鄺俊宇所講: 呢場運動每一位巴絲打都唔想失去，每一位都好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZvBa3x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZvBa3x.png&h=0388073f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但今次好不幸地，喺上星期六，我地眾多義士之一「杰仔」梁凌杰義士犧牲咗自己嘅生命以喚醒香港人上街抗爭，最終有近二百萬香港人踏足港島，團結一致地向政府表達抗爭四大目的：撤回惡法、反對定性暴動、追究警察暴行、撤銷控罪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NZeG98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NZeG98.jpg&h=7b1f268e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMbddgP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMbddgP.jpg&h=53e0a205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(未FACT CHECK 係咪真係梁義士)<br />\n<br />\n可惜去到最後，政府依然無回應過其中一個訴求，只係縮喺政總唔願面對民眾。雖然係咁，希望大家都唔好咁快麻木退縮，不論進退都好，謹記香港曾經有人願意為呢個地方獻上生命。係日後面對社會不公不義之事，繼續企出黎發聲、爭取、抗爭，不撤不散。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家有時間，希望大家可以係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日頭七／或公祭時</span>，到現場<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">送義士最後一程</span>，到時衣著建議以<span style=\"color: red;\">素黑為主</span>，可以嘅話著埋<span style=\"color: red;\">黃色雨褸</span>，戴上<span style=\"color: red;\">防護口罩眼罩</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">手持鮮花雨傘</span>去悼念梁義士，咁亦為防有特發情況時，可以遮擋暴雨同保護自己同同伴。<br />\n<br />\n亦更希望呢套裝束成為我地喺今日、聽日、日後嘅一種象徵物、埋下憧景未來嘅一粒種子。因為咁樣，先至會令梁義士嘅犧牲更有意義。<br />\n<br />\n最後，抱歉讓你孤單中離開，悼念香港人梁凌杰義士 (1984-2019)。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/21/170134_0cff9910eba93618e39618e3941b5afc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F21%2F170134_0cff9910eba93618e39618e3941b5afc.png&h=c59c3fb3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YiuN2aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYiuN2aa.jpg&h=560df379&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a60b3dd25396f9ba315aabe260a7760b264f7b3c","tid":1247894,"uid":59693,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:28:10.000Z","msg":"其實當講到抗爭運動象徵物／精神物方面，有套電影嘅內容係非常之接近香港社會發生緊嘅事，叫「V for Vendetta」，中文叫V煞。套戲主要講民眾運動點樣覺醒，從而反對極權政府。<br />\n<br />\n當中最出名當然應該係用係唔同遊行運動之中嘅V煞面具。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykWpj41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FykWpj41.jpg&h=b2032ad4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重有2019年都用得返嘅嘅對白:<br />\nV for Vendetta - Ideas are Bulletproof<br />\nBehind this mask there is more than just flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea... and ideas are bulletproof<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r10SnWneyGw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dr10SnWneyGw&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOe2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=93ce5112\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r10SnWneyGw</a><br />\n<br />\nV for Vendetta - Speech<br />\nBut if you see what I see ,   if you feel as I feel,   and if you would seek as I seek,   then I ask you to stand beside me<br />\n如果你感受的 與我感受的一樣 如果你尋求的 與我尋求的一樣 請你站到我這邊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PtJCrnZQ9iU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPtJCrnZQ9iU&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOe2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=0405e4f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PtJCrnZQ9iU</a><br />\n<br />\nV嘅面具係套戲入面揭開咗抗爭嘅序幕，民眾亦用面具統一左套戲嘅中心思想，Beneath this mask there is an idea。<br />\n<br />\n所以，只要香港人都有呢個理念，其實黃雨褸下，每個人都係梁義士。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QDKVrK1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQDKVrK1.png&h=d9f5f215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知大家都點睇？"},{"pid":"16fc7c408edd6410a8691dba4e922d15b06ca839","tid":1247894,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3434de58a0a61399141fa250bf6c168a9eb10ba","tid":1247894,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:39:12.000Z","msg":"the seed"},{"pid":"9301bd704f27a2784beb500b70f5cca9a05b19a5","tid":1247894,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d1cf1ee460751a56c0321ed3ab4941ae2144fd","tid":1247894,"uid":11827,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06ae3e02a1f2931502ab530ad16091416c134ed","tid":1247894,"uid":185789,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:53:51.000Z","msg":"又黎情感勒索<br />\n<br />\n左膠食夠人血饅頭未?"},{"pid":"65fa59ff66e138f09b3926390069f5514444a45c","tid":1247894,"uid":84267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f06ae3e02a1f2931502ab530ad16091416c134ed","tid":1247894,"uid":185789,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:53:51.000Z","msg":"又黎情感勒索<br />\n<br />\n左膠食夠人血饅頭未?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:01:05.000Z","msg":"情感乜撚勒索呀<br />\n左乜撚膠, 人乜撚血饅頭呀屌你老母<br />\n依家開個post悼念下烈士都要有你呢D垃圾分化撚入嚟"},{"pid":"307058ed4c544914e2bf159ff6caa1319e355030","tid":1247894,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bedc95a446e9b53b5505a8a56a849991c27bf9e0","tid":1247894,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:19:36.000Z","msg":"一路好走，我哋一定一定唔會忘記你為呢個地方獻出咗最寶貴嘅生命。"},{"pid":"c7df0ec517b753d3a760066467a7bcaa030e52b2","tid":1247894,"uid":212843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f06ae3e02a1f2931502ab530ad16091416c134ed","tid":1247894,"uid":185789,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:53:51.000Z","msg":"又黎情感勒索<br />\n<br />\n左膠食夠人血饅頭未?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:20:31.000Z","msg":"ON99"},{"pid":"9ea6e284cf3be68890f149225e1c7f6fa751a9d0","tid":1247894,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4004a91398c4db16edb9081dfd8191c714a75161","tid":1247894,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:31:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a3d55305bbb96e4514893134634c32f744ab2356","tid":1247894,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:32:27.000Z","msg":"one for all<br />\n<br />\nall for one"},{"pid":"18c5fa4c86c06ac3b3d96bfdd528ac85895ef533","tid":1247894,"uid":59693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pish"},{"pid":"1dd7484e278f53f1f57078b4bef908944022ae3f","tid":1247894,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"94f12c653e3ed01464a335af00994627f2a4f982","tid":1247894,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:43:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d183c36683a453de503bce7a0eb40c845a2ff2","tid":1247894,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家快啲出黎送別"},{"pid":"a0b6c1033e0063aaec8d5d298c